VPNaaS: Remove methods, once router object available

The following methods were moved from the L3 agent, and placed in
the VPNService class to decouple the device driver from the L3 agent:
    def get_namespace(self, router_id):
    def add_nat_rule(self, router_id, chain, rule, top=False):
    def remove_nat_rule(self, router_id, chain, rule, top=False):
    def iptables_apply(self, router_id):

This commit (currently), is a placeholder so that we remove these methods,
once there is a 'router' instance available that the device drivers can use.
As part of the removal, some of the logic will move into the device driver,
and some may end up in the router class?

